[Webhook/Syslog Trigger]
        │
        ▼
[Parse & Normalize Log]
→ Chuẩn hóa format: timestamp, src_ip, 
  dst_ip, protocol, event_type, severity
        │
        ▼
[Enrich Data]
→ Gọi AbuseIPDB API kiểm tra IP reputation
→ Gọi pfSense API lấy thêm context
        │
        ▼
[Classify Event - Switch Node]
→ event_type = "IDS_ALERT" / "PORT_SCAN" 
  / "BRUTE_FORCE"     → WF-01
→ event_type = "HIGH_BANDWIDTH" 
  / "CONN_FLOOD"      → WF-02
→ event_type = "NEW_MAC" 
  / "UNKNOWN_DEVICE"  → WF-03
→ event_type = "VPN_TUNNEL_DOWN"          → WF-04
→ Không khớp         → Log & discard
